the seaside resort that once looked 
to mayor james l usry to end a legacy of corruption has seen him 
and 13 others charged in conspiracies that include bribes illegal 
gifts and extortion 
the city council president and zoning board chairman also were 
among those arrested on corruption charges thursday after an 
eightmonth state investigation a 14th person has not yet been 
arrested 
weve been the laughingstock of the country for a long time 
