on wednesday us district judge howard mckibben gave maddox 
permission to drop charges against the two remaining defendants in 
a muchpublicized case that grew from the suspected slaughter of 
some 600 mustangs in central nevada 
dave morehead and shannon brennan were scheduled to go on trial 
aug 8 
i just took a very critical look at the case and in my 
