boost the partys waning popularity ahead of multiparty elections 
they will be hungarys first free general elections since 1947 
the budapest meeting comes as polands communist party central 
committee holds crucial talks to decide its future after a similar 
experiment led to devastating election defeats poles 
overwhelmingly supported independent solidarityled candidates 
