at 7257 cents a pound feeder cattle were unchanged to 40 cent 
lower with august at 8307 cents a pound live hogs were 27 cent 
lower to 10 cent higher with august at 4605 cents a pound frozen 
pork bellies were 122 cents lower to 25 cent higher with august 
